{"tid":2263903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府推自願性行蹤記錄app","createTime":"2020-10-30T08:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T11:56:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":165,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"3d3b8cef3665f69bf662dd551da745fa6113cfa7","tid":2263903,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"政府抗疫app名為「安心出行」 市民商戶可自願參與<br />\n<br />\n政府招標製作感染風險通知流動應用程式，讓市民記錄行蹤，預計快將推出。程式將名為「安心出行」，場所營運者和市民均為自願參與，市民到訪場所時可以掃描二維碼，記錄行程，商戶亦可記錄訪客到訪，如有關場所出現感染個案，用戶會獲得通知。為作試點推行，康文署已提供164個室內設施張貼二維碼，包括115間體育館和45個游泳池等；食環署則有97個場所，包括熟食市場和街市。<br />\n<br />\n程式將可於蘋果、安卓和華為的平台下載。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2364003&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=800e74ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364003</a>"},{"pid":"fcfc4d9d2132d5970cd7ec71f668fd6da2680d01","tid":2263903,"uid":196924,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"學人追蹤但係連GPS都冇<br />\n就咁scan QR code 儲落db就完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324cd59b78da0fc8fb52f164d248742e0558467c","tid":2263903,"uid":8014,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"藍絲：無著數 點解要裝 點解要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c3ac3f72f0b3d3335b1835eba1416593d15ad3","tid":2263903,"uid":323740,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:30:18.000Z","msg":"如果配合埋其他商店有優惠會更加吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5426212b158349b39d64f74d8e496d37410ae51","tid":2263903,"uid":17641,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"可以偽造證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"